flowchart TD
    A[Server-Rendered HTML Displayed in Browser] --> B[JavaScript Bundle Downloaded]
    B --> C[Deserialize Dehydrated State from Script Tag]
    C --> D[Framework Starts Hydration Walk]
    D --> E[Match DOM Nodes to Component Tree]
    E --> F{DOM matches expected output?}
    F -- No --> G[Log Hydration Mismatch Warning]
    G --> H[Replace Mismatched Subtree]
    F -- Yes --> I[Reuse Existing DOM Nodes]
    H --> J[Attach Event Listeners to Nodes]
    I --> J
    J --> K[Restore Reactive State]
    K --> L[Run Mounted and useEffect Callbacks]
    L --> M[Page Fully Interactive]
    style A fill:#3b82f6,color:#fff
    style M fill:#22c55e,color:#fff
